HEADWORD: Aground
<hw>A*ground"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv. & a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>a-</ets> + <ets>ground</ets>.]</ety> <def>On the ground; stranded;
-- a nautical term applied to a ship when its bottom lodges on the
ground.</def> <rj><au>Totten.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
